name: Fxos-dashboard
tagline: Dashboard app for Mozilla Firefox OS.
body:
### Welcome to Firefox OS Dashboard app page
This app allows you to monitor the number of blockers for each version of Firefox OS. If you have a Firefox OS device, please visit this URL to install the app:

http://halolo.com/Mozilla/FxOS_install.html 

### Support or Contact
Questions? Please contact Kevin Hu(khu@mozilla.com), Senior manager, engineering project management, Mozilla.
